<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Woof & Wander</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container mt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-8 offset-md-2">
                <div class="card shadow-lg">
                    <div class="card-header bg-primary text-white text-center">
                        <h1>About Us</h1>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-body">
                        <p class="lead">
                            Welcome to <strong>Woof & Wander</strong> — a friendly and fun dog breed meet-up community
                            for pet lovers across Northern Ireland and Ireland!
                        </p>

                        <p>
                            Whether you're a new dog owner or a seasoned pet parent, Woof and Wander offers a space to
                            connect,
                            explore, and create wonderful memories with your canine companions. We believe that
                            everything is better with friends — especially the furry kind!
                        </p>

                        <h3 class="mt-4">What We Offer:</h3>
                        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
                            <li class="list-group-item">
                                <i class="bi bi-calendar-event"> </i><strong>Event Calendar:</strong> Find exciting dog
                                meet-ups happening near you — from group walks along scenic trails to fun social events
                                with fellow dog owners.
                            </li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">
                                <i class="bi bi-chat-left-dots"> </i><strong>Community Forum:</strong> Get advice, ask questions, and share your
                                experiences in our friendly community forum.
                            </li>
                            <li class="list-group-item">
                                <i class="bi bi-camera-fill"></i></i> <strong>Event Gallery:</strong> View photos from
                                past events and upload your own memories! See the joy in every wagging tail.
                            </li>
                        </ul>

                        <h3 class="mt-4">Why Join Woof & Wander?</h3>
                        <p>
                            We know that life is better when shared — with both people and pets. By joining our
                            community, you'll gain access to:
                        </p>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Exclusive event calendars and meet-ups.</li>
                            <li>A network of fellow dog lovers.</li>
                            <li>The ability to share your experiences through photos and discussions.</li>
                        </ul>

                        <div class="text-center mt-4">
                            <a class="btn btn-primary btn-lg" asp-controller="User" asp-action="Register">Join the
                                Community</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>

</html>
